    "name": "Tempo Punk",
    "steam_appid": 1868430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/862f1cbdbe55d520f139afb29475cd65.poster.avif?t=1758830137\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/862f1cbdbe55d520f139afb29475cd65.webm?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/862f1cbdbe55d520f139afb29475cd65.mp4?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是C3V1N，一个被困在反乌托邦大都会“先锋市”中的破损清洁单元。伴随着每一次节拍，你奋力搏杀，突出重围——每一次射击都必须精准命中节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/dd7269e7ea63d02dd3ae7f678d2038a3.poster.avif?t=1758830137\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/dd7269e7ea63d02dd3ae7f678d2038a3.webm?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/dd7269e7ea63d02dd3ae7f678d2038a3.mp4?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的力量与节奏休戚相关。射击、冲刺、装弹——这些动作只有与心跳般悸动的电子乐同步，才能释放毁灭性的伤害，让你于枪林弹雨中存活。一旦错过节拍，便将承受致命后果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在激烈的手工打造关卡中将你的技巧推向极限，并直面巨大的生物机械头目。精进你的通关技巧，攀登全球排行榜，将你的名字铭刻在这座赛博朋克都市“先锋市”的数字编年史中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏原声带是一场残酷的电子乐盛宴，但你的个人音乐库才是真正的军火库。革命性的音乐导入功能让你能将任何歌曲变为武器，并在程序生成的关卡中亲身感受歌曲的情绪渐强与节奏骤降。伴随你自选的狂暴节拍，系统性瓦解企业机器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/0e28c5470c5b20e8475ad979b84b9d94.poster.avif?t=1758830137\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/0e28c5470c5b20e8475ad979b84b9d94.webm?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/0e28c5470c5b20e8475ad979b84b9d94.mp4?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先锋市是一个由金属与罪恶构成的垂死世界。通过粗野主义的赛博朋克建筑和炫目的视觉特效，亲身体验一场贯穿这座反乌托邦大都会的、令人血脉偾张的高能战役。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>节拍永不停止。你亦永不停歇。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/4a64ca74a55e0606dd5c1222e9a08c87.poster.avif?t=1758830137\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/4a64ca74a55e0606dd5c1222e9a08c87.webm?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868430/extras/4a64ca74a55e0606dd5c1222e9a08c87.mp4?t=1758830137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
